5. Layout of TaliesinPHP(tm)
----------------------------

    5.1 TaliesinPHP(tm) - Directory Structure
    -----------------------------------------
    
    taliesin
     |- extlib
     |   |- geshi
     |   |- RedBean
     |- lib
         |- DBAdapter.php
         |- Base.php
         |- Command.php
         |- Controller.php
         |- Dispatcher.php
         |- UrlParser.php
         |- View.php
    
    5.2 TaliesinPHP(tm) - Typical App Directory Structure
    -----------------------------------------------------
    
    appname
     |- app
     |   |- controllers
     |   |- layouts
     |   |- models
     |   |- views
     |- docroot
     |   |- assets
     |   |   |- css
     |   |   |- images
     |   |   |- js
     |   |- .htaccess
     |   |- index.php
     |- docs
     |- taliesin
     |   |- extlib
     |   |- lib
     |- sql
     |- config.php
     |- bootstrap.php

